How to install node on Linux

(see https://askubuntu.com/questions/898379/how-does-tar-command-work-for-installing-node-js/898385)


cd /usr
wget https://nodejs.org/dist/v8.9.3/node-v8.9.3-linux-x64.tar.xz
tar --strip-components=1 -xf /usr/node-v8.9.3-linux-x64.tar.xz

close shell and reopen with new shell

whereis